org.opt4j.benchmarks.knapsack

Class KnapsackProfitEvaluator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opt4j.benchmarks.knapsack.KnapsackProfitEvaluator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Evaluator<ItemSelection>

    public class KnapsackProfitEvaluator
extends java.lang.Object
implements Evaluator<ItemSelection>
    The KnapsackProfitEvaluator evaluates a given ItemSelection using one Objective to sum up all knapsack overloads and one Objective for the profit of each knapsack.
